{"tid":1682850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【國際戰線】英國下議院通過12月12號舉行大選","createTime":"2019-10-30T10:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T12:07:37.000Z","uid":32204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3d8d3d9af68134b95ea8b694b1ee5d382b829196","tid":1682850,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"因為國會 deadlock 搞到脫極都脫唔到歐嘅英國終於舉行大選<br />\n如果保守黨加脫歐黨嬴到大比數議席就可以令日後脫歐順利好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBBC 汁 : <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-50229318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-50229318&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt32WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=fdf068ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-50229318&h=9c3aea4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-50229318</a><br />\n<br />\n而如果大家係 BNO / BC，可以透過捐錢去畀意見啲政黨。支持 BNO 平權又好，全體香港人第二公民身份又好，甚至想要英國版人權法，都可以做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加香港需要嘅係更多盟友，多一位議員幫手就多一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃世澤教學汁 : <a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/29381/%e7%94%a8%e6%94%bf%e6%b2%bb%e7%8d%bb%e9%87%91%e5%b9%ab-bno\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F29381%2F%25e7%2594%25a8%25e6%2594%25bf%25e6%25b2%25bb%25e7%258d%25bb%25e9%2587%2591%25e5%25b9%25ab-bno&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt32WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=e6335459\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/29381/%e7%94%a8%e6%94%bf%e6%b2%bb%e7%8d%bb%e9%87%91%e5%b9%ab-bno</a>"},{"pid":"2f695142fcf369f1366c6fa88315fb028a2160a7","tid":1682850,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:06:04.000Z","msg":"已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /Task1</span></span><